FuncDef: The display hwtacacs-server accounting-stop-packet command displays information about Accounting-Stop packets sent by an HWTACACS server. The display hwtacacs-server accounting-stop-packet command displays information about Accounting-Stop packets sent by an HWTACACS server.

ParaDef.Info:
Specifies the start number of the Accounting-Stop packets to be displayed.
The value is an integer ranging from 1 to 65535.

Displays information about Accounting-Stop packets sent by the HWTACACS server with a specified IPv4 address.
The value is in dotted decimal notation.
